OL,4,G0115FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GCraig's brother Brent borrows a
OL,6,     Glogging machine, leading to a
OL,7,     Grisky mountainside recovery;
OL,8,     Gveteran log hauler Dan Millar
OL,9,     Gbattles rough roads and torn up
OL,10,     Gtires to make it to the mill.
OL,11,G0210FMud Mountain Haulers
