OL,13,     Gleaves Craig frustrated by
OL,14,     Gendless breakdowns; a driver
OL,15,     Gfights a back injury to keep the
OL,16,     Gtrucks moving and a log hauler's
OL,17,     Gcrash sparks an all-night rescue.
